  "body": "In a few places in the application there are some issues with the bottom sheet.\n\n\nIn general the bottom sheet height should fit to its content. If there is more content than a whole screen the bottom sheet should be able to scroll.\n\n\nIn this example the bottom sheet should also be slightly higher, i.e we increase the max size of the bottom sheet.\n![Movie_Recording_2023-05-30_11-50-48](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/22799766/9d681efd-a7d8-4919-a063-8e01fbf36ba4)\n\n\nAlso check background color in dark mode. It might need blur",
